  "texts": [
    "Column (8) of Table 4 shows the corresponding regression results.",
    "Based on these results, we can conclude that the issuance of green bonds significantly reduces the environmental penalty imposed on enterprises.",
    "This test further confirms that the issuance of green bonds enhances enterprises' ER from an objective perspective.",
    "The ER undertaken by enterprises may be affected by some unobserved industry-specific trends before the issuance of bonds.",
    "ER in different industries may have different time trends."
  ]
